    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>178</ID>
      <DefaultText>Vostiel grumbles but obeys, and has the device uncrated and on its mount by the time the rest of the squad readies itself for a counterattack. The difficult part is getting the weapon into range without being spotted, but you manage to run it in between patrols and set it up just behind the ridge so only the muzzle is showing.

